{"tid":904144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而我不知道吳靄儀是誰 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2018-11-16T05:54:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T10:29:32.000Z","uid":138409,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"00f6992221dd9a989b420e5ff36999b9387d6ee5","tid":904144,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:54:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20181114/20545187?fbclid=IwAR2q_U9a-FNTH3Mqb3Nm0b1xsdSKo7PC3xZAJOmAa5skzHs0_Zw5DpcIHQI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181114%2F20545187%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2q_U9a-FNTH3Mqb3Nm0b1xsdSKo7PC3xZAJOmAa5skzHs0_Zw5DpcIHQI&d=38jqZUFrbngVAerxXx0BO57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=53b7f1bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181114%2F20545187%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2q_U9a-FNTH3Mqb3Nm0b1xsdSKo7PC3xZAJOmAa5skzHs0_Zw5DpcIHQI&h=d9913464\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20181114/20545187?fbclid=IwAR2q_U9a-FNTH3Mqb3Nm0b1xsdSKo7PC3xZAJOmAa5skzHs0_Zw5DpcIHQI</a><br />\n那天下午去聽吳靄儀講座，早上內子跟四位街坊閒聊。內子說「陣間去聽吳靄儀」，眾人齊問：「邊個係吳靄儀？」這幾個街坊是我們樓下小店的兼職店員，全是土生土長女孩，三個剛大學畢業，一個還在讀書。我恰巧在場，震驚到一個點，彷彿聽到有人鄭重地跟我說「地球是平的」。<br />\n我在她們那個年紀的時候，已看過吳靄儀寫金庸小說的書；她做過近廿年立法會議員，上過無數次電視；最近金庸逝世，她寫的悼文仍然在Facebook瘋傳。凡此種種使我不期然相信，吳靄儀即使未至於家傳戶曉，在香港也該算廣為人知。為什麼這幾個廿多歲的大學畢業生，統統聞所未聞？是活在平行時空嗎？於是我大膽做了個實驗，令我確信平行時空是真的。我問：「聽過梁家傑未？」最初都是滿頭黑人問號，突然有一位興奮喊道：「好似係好耐之前上電視教英文嗰個！」新一代居然有人知道史前的劉家傑，令我懷疑那是前世記憶的有力證據，可惜我問的是梁家傑。一不做二不休，我索性窮追猛打：「馬建，馬凱，姜濤，吳亦凡，識邊幾個？」<span style=\"color: red;\">姜濤和吳亦凡，如我所料，人人皆知。馬凱有一人認識。但聽過馬建的，一個也沒有，是一個也沒有！</span><br />\n要區別人與機器，我知道可利用「圖靈測試」（Turing test）；若想區分不同世代或不同知識面的人，是否可進行「吳靄儀測試」（Margaret Test）呢？這幾天我承認已沉迷於「吳靄儀測試」，名單還加入湯家驊。朋友幫我問了六位中六男生，<span style=\"color: red;\">結果是：六人皆認識吳亦凡；四人認識姜濤和湯家驊；三人認識梁家傑；一人聽過馬凱；沒有人聽過馬建和吳靄儀。還有以下彩蛋：有人問「吳靄儀係咪明星」，有人說「佢呢啲建制派我唔識㗎喎」。問他們怎麼認識湯家驊，原來因為「佢成日上電視受訪」。但沒有人聽過「十一哥」。</span><br />\n今天談社會或政治問題，比貧富懸殊更嚴重的，也許是知識懸殊。大眾接收資訊的渠道千差萬別，於是便有了平行時空，結果所有人都在同一個現實呼吸，在不同的世界做夢。"},{"pid":"c8b179d63422ec9b7835e7637445c6a876794570","tid":904144,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:57:54.000Z","msg":"「十一哥」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3725c92f38e1597477b7d065fe4df51545d3da7","tid":904144,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:59:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8acd8c7a8e43a420ff8f7241928ba9252dc6b5e0","tid":904144,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:00:03.000Z","msg":"唔睇新聞嘅結果<br />\n姜濤又係乜水"},{"pid":"ce1af4fddd60b66abcca20dad1bce5d68be6ce79","tid":904144,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8b179d63422ec9b7835e7637445c6a876794570","tid":904144,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:57:54.000Z","msg":"「十一哥」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5143034c32b397cf7695e1bf99c83e0eedc05bbf","tid":904144,"uid":49197,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:01:26.000Z","msg":"我問：「聽過梁家傑未？」最初都是滿頭黑人問號，突然有一位興奮喊道：「好似係好耐之前上電視教英文嗰個！」新一代居然有人知道史前的劉家傑，令我懷疑那是前世記憶的有力證據，可惜我問的是梁家傑。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df3e412d8d4ee3ce79f688105902a7a3a7b681e","tid":904144,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:01:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"79433c9f2d00955a4a915330f92f166fa2ab89c3","tid":904144,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:02:29.000Z","msg":"姜濤係邊位？ 真心唔識"},{"pid":"dbafa3d1ede5149a4f4192db156aba99ea8514aa","tid":904144,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:03:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>六人皆認識吳亦凡；四人認識姜濤和湯家驊；三人認識梁家傑；一人聽過馬凱；沒有人聽過馬建和吳靄儀。還有以下彩蛋：有人問「吳靄儀係咪明星」，有人說「佢呢啲建制派我唔識㗎喎」。問他們怎麼認識湯家驊，原來因為「佢成日上電視受訪」。但沒有人聽過「十一哥」。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n主要關乎CCTVB"},{"pid":"dce471aa5d1211d1de01374a6216f47cae0f7d97","tid":904144,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce1af4fddd60b66abcca20dad1bce5d68be6ce79","tid":904144,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8b179d63422ec9b7835e7637445c6a876794570","tid":904144,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:57:54.000Z","msg":"「十一哥」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f0a5049974227d962f48c8d5e857a967092d77","tid":904144,"uid":47005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:09:54.000Z","msg":"其實無聽過黃洋達係咪正常&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"bc4a774ef10d1f8063d8a6e1f516e8e0dba70425","tid":904144,"uid":192068,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-